				<div id="post-5732" class="post-5732 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-survival-preparedness tag-lifestyle-design tag-permaculture">
					<h1 class="entry-title">Episode-802- Permaculture Misconception vs. Reality</h1>

					<div class="entry-meta">
						<span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/permaculture-misconception-vs-reality" title="12:03 pm" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">December 13, 2011</span></a> <span class="byline"><span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/author/Modern Survival" title="View all posts by Modern Survival">Modern Survival</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><span class="meta-sep">|</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/permaculture-misconception-vs-reality#comments" title="Comment on Episode-802- Permaculture Misconception vs. Reality">19 Comments</a></span>
											</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

					<div class="entry-content">
						<div id="tweetbutton5732" class="tw_button" style="float:right;margin-left:10px;"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Fpermaculture-misconception-vs-reality&amp;text=Episode-802-%20Permaculture%20Misconception%20vs.%20Reality&amp;related=&amp;lang=en&amp;count=horizontal&amp;counturl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Fpermaculture-misconception-vs-reality" class="twitter-share-button"  style="width:55px;height:22px;background:transparent url('http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-tweet-button/tweetn.png') no-repeat  0 0;text-align:left;text-indent:-9999px;display:block;">Tweet</a></div><div class="podPress_content podPress_content_audio_mp3">
